{"tid":977902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［廢佬系列］咁樣等車有咩出奇","createTime":"2019-01-11T13:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T13:43:27.000Z","uid":149515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eca81e356de9c55d3f8e716a4b5af9bd95f91d4a","tid":977902,"uid":149515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"前面白衫個女人同再前面個細路女應該係佢個老婆同女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢老婆一直睥佢 叫佢咪咁坐<br />\n個廢佬不時撩下個女玩 叫佢一齊坐 個女(著小學校服裙)又真係坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....佢老母又冇強硬阻止...<br />\n有一下同個女玩 個女手上個公仔仲碌左出馬路邊 細路女即刻望都唔望烏個身出去執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好在個時馬路係紅燈 冇車駛過<br />\n<br />\n聽到個廢佬大聲同佢老婆講：「你講話走好耐啦 又唔走 我坐下都唔得呀」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲路人行過都望幾望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左窮人之外，痴線佬都咪鬼生/同佢生啦 一啲意識都冇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/11/213230_e85203cd14a4c636c8184ae1d5df4a93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2F213230_e85203cd14a4c636c8184ae1d5df4a93.png&h=585e8452&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}